.TH KINGPEPE 1
.SH NAME
kingpepe \- command dispatcher for KingPepe Core utilities
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kingpepe
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fICOMMAND\fR [\fIARGS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B kingpepe
utility dispatches to KingPepe Core command-line tools such as
.BR kingpeped ,
.BR kingpepe-cli ,
.BR kingpepe-wallet ,
.BR kingpepe-tx ,
and
.BR kingpepe-util .
.SH OPTIONS
Run
.B kingpepe -help
for the complete option list supported by this build.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kingpeped (1),
.BR kingpepe-cli (1),
.BR kingpepe-qt (1)
